    </head>
    <body class="homeBody caudalieGame">
        <content tag="content">
			<style>
				.innerContainer {
					padding:0 34px;
					background: white;
				}
				h1 {
					color:#b45383;
					font-size:31px;
					font-weight:bold;
					font-family: Arial;
					font-style: normal;
					margin-top:20px;
				}
				.info div {
					float:left;
					width:47%;
				}
				.info img {
					margin-left:30px;
				}
				.info h3 {
					font-weight:bold;
					font-family: Arial;
					font-style: normal;
					font-size:21px;
					color:#676767;
					margin: 10px 0 0 0;
					padding: 0;
					line-height: normal;
				}
				.info p {
					color:#676767;
					font-size:14px;
				}
				.game p {
					margin: 0;
					padding: 0;
				}
				.game div {
					float:left;
					width:27%;
					margin: 0 7px;
					-moz-border-radius:5px;
					-webkit-border-radius:5px;
					border-radius:5px;
					background:#f0f0f0;
					padding:20px;
					color:#666;
					height:245px;
				}
				.game div.full {
					width:95%;
				}
				.game .step {
					font-size:52px;
					color:#dd82a2;
					font-weight:bold;
					margin: 0;
					line-height:45px;
					padding: 0 0 15px 0;
				}
				.game .stepInfo {
					font-size:52px;
					color:#dd82a2;
				}
				.game .answer {
					margin-bottom:5px;
				}
				.game .like{
					background: white;
					-moz-border-radius:5px;
					-webkit-border-radius:5px;
					border-radius:5px;
					margin: 10px 0;
					padding: 3px 5px;
				}
				.game .like span {
					float:right;
					margin-top:3px;
				}
				.game .like p {
					float:left;
					margin-top:3px;
				}
				.game .question {
					margin:0 0 10px 0;
				}
				.game .emailField {
					border: 3px solid #ababab;
					width:96.1%;
					margin: 5px 0 10px 0;
					background: white;
				}
				.game .gameApprove input {
					float:left;
					width:10%;

				}
				.game .gameApprove label {
					float:left;
					width:85%;
					margin-left:3px;
					font-size:12px;
				}
				.game .submit {
					float:right;
					border: none;
					font-size:16px;
					font-weight:bold;
					background:#b65586;
					background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #e38da9, #b65586);
					background-image: -webkit-gradient(linear, center top, center bottom, from(#e38da9), to(#b65586));
					background-image: -o-linear-gradient(top, #e38da9, #b65586);
					background-image: linear-gradient(top, #e38da9, #b65586);
					color:white;
					padding: 3px 8px;
					margin-top:5px;
				}
				.bottomContent {
					-moz-border-radius:5px;
					-webkit-border-radius:5px;
					border-radius:5px;
					padding: 30px;
					margin-top:20px;
					color:white;
					background:url(/images/products/caudalie_gameBG.jpg) no-repeat bottom black;
					min-height:1210px;
				}
				.bottomContent div {
					float:left;
					width:50%;
				}
				.bottomContent h3 {
					color:white;
					font-size:28px;
					font-family: Arial;
					margin: 0;
					padding: 0;
				}
				.testimonials {
					width:350px !important;
					margin-left:40px;
				}
				.testimonials .testimonial {
					font-size:16px;
					font-style:italic;
					font-weight:bold;
					text-align: center;
					margin-bottom:20px;
				}
				.testimonials .testimonial span {
					display:block;
					color:#dc80a1;
					font-style:normal;
					font-weight:normal;
					margin-top:8px;
				}
				.moreInfo {
					clear:both;
					text-align: center;
					font-size:14px;
					padding-top:40px;
				}
				.moreInfo a, .moreInfo a:visited {
					font-weight:bold;
					color:#dc80a1;
					text-decoration: none;
				}
			</style>

			<div class="innerContainer">

				<g:link mapping="brandGB" params="[normalisedBrandName:'caudalie']"><r:img dir="/images/brands/l/caudalie.png"/></g:link>

				<h1>WIN a fabulous 5 piece set from Caudalie (worth over £120)</h1>
				<div class="info clearfix">
					<div>
						<h3>There is no better way to show your skin some winter love.</h3>
						<p>You may have noticed that it's getting cold outside! And while you're all busy bundling up in scarves and mittens, your face is hardly getting any love! In fact, you're probably leaving your skin to face those freezing temperatures all alone and unprotected!</p>
						<p>Not to worry, we're not suggesting that you wear a face mitten (cause that would be, um, ridiculous). Instead, we've teamed up with Caudalie to give you the chance to <strong>win one of 15 complete sets</strong> of Caudalie's ultra hydrating and nourishing Vinosource products.</p>
						<p>For every 50 Likes, we will give away: Caudalie's Quenching Sorbet-Crème, Nourishing Concentrate, Anti-wrinkle Nourishing Cream, Anti-Wrinkle Ultra-Nourishing Cream and Moisturizing Cream-Mask. All products are <strong>full size</strong>.</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<g:link mapping="brandGB" params="[normalisedBrandName:'caudalie']"><r:img dir="/images/products/caudalie_game.jpg"/></g:link>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div id="question" class="game clearfix"><g:render template="caudalieQuestion"/></div>
				<div class="bottomContent clearfix">
					<div>
						<h3>Video</h3>
						<p>Hear from Caudalie co-founder Mathilde Thomas what her Quenching Sorbet-Crème is all about -French accent included!</p>
						<iframe width="415" height="241" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/Mpz_LKDLouA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonials">
						<h3>Sounds like we're not the only ones who love Caudalie!</h3>
						<p class="testimonial">"I have A new boyfriend... CAUDALIE PARIS. I love it! It's amazing. Its so moisturing but yet drys on your skin so fast. It absorbs so quickly deep into your skin and leaves no greasy due." <span>Beauty Junkies Opinions</span></p>
						<p class="testimonial">"I used it last night and my skin felt lovely and soft this morning. I'm already considering buying the full size once I've used up this sample." <span>Ace Stace Beauty</span></p>
					</div>
					<p class="moreInfo">For more information please visit <g:link url="http://www.caudalie.com/uk/">www.caudalie.com</g:link></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</content>
    </body>
</html>